    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/2e412b10689320833c8d4dbdfb2981c0.poster.avif?t=1676352583\" width=622 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/2e412b10689320833c8d4dbdfb2981c0.webm?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/2e412b10689320833c8d4dbdfb2981c0.mp4?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>来自开发者的话：<br>玩家爸爸们好，我们是来自成都的Funshine，<br>这两年所有兄弟在疫情和资方的高压下，终于在饥寒交迫中将游戏给拉扯出来，一路上困难重重竟也不知从何说起。好在作品终于要见天了，无论结果是好是坏对团队辛苦的大家来说也算是个交代。项目目前处于最后的测试调优阶段，相信不久后就会与大家见面，感谢所有人长期以来一路的支持！也欢迎所有玩家提出宝贵的建议帮助我们进步。（虽然这个作品很多地方在我们看来还跟屎一样，但团队没钱只能硬着头皮上了，没办法，挨喷就挨喷吧...）<br>我是Taki，有问题可以绕开其他成员直接骂我，下有联系方式。<br><br>QQ交流1群：584823151<br>QQ：786591667<br>Twitter：Taki_yuan<br>wechat：Taki-Nan<br><br>———————————————————————————————————————————————————————————<br>《JO JO WO》是一款欢乐的多人对战游戏。游戏中分为“参赛者”、“叛徒”、“小丑”三个阵营，<br>“参赛者”阵营需要完成主线任务成功逃生获得胜利，“叛徒”阵营需要消灭所有其他玩家获得胜利，“小丑”阵营需要完成主线任务独自逃生获得胜利<br>玩家需要根据自己所在的阵营，完成指定的阵营任务，赢得比赛胜利。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/21e6e33348a64b3bd14568aec7c2602f.poster.avif?t=1676352583\" width=638 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/21e6e33348a64b3bd14568aec7c2602f.webm?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/21e6e33348a64b3bd14568aec7c2602f.mp4?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>选择职业：<br>除了不同的阵营拥有不同的技能以外，不同的职业也拥有不同的职业技能，请选择合适你阵营的职业以帮助你完成任务。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/48136e7d6e52bcd5dbb04ba7dc12581b.poster.avif?t=1676352583\" width=638 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/48136e7d6e52bcd5dbb04ba7dc12581b.webm?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/48136e7d6e52bcd5dbb04ba7dc12581b.mp4?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>修理发电机：<br>修理所有的发电机，激活通讯站，逃出生天！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/ea93d1e4fda2f3057d557d38d20f0acf.poster.avif?t=1676352583\" width=636 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/ea93d1e4fda2f3057d557d38d20f0acf.webm?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/ea93d1e4fda2f3057d557d38d20f0acf.mp4?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>rougelike卡牌：<br>rougelike卡牌会给你不同的效果，选择合适的rougelike卡牌，你会更加容易获得胜利。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/dadf912b37a33660edd643707bbe3ac1.poster.avif?t=1676352583\" width=638 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/dadf912b37a33660edd643707bbe3ac1.webm?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/dadf912b37a33660edd643707bbe3ac1.mp4?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>投票：<br>票选出你认为可疑的玩家，将他逐出基地，用基地外的恶劣环境制裁他。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/b7fdd4484529ebab3626ad0c69ce8f0d.poster.avif?t=1676352583\" width=638 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/b7fdd4484529ebab3626ad0c69ce8f0d.webm?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/b7fdd4484529ebab3626ad0c69ce8f0d.mp4?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>逃出生天：<br>点亮通讯塔，呼叫直升机，逃出生天<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/283e30ddfd354a30d0149a4202498271.poster.avif?t=1676352583\" width=638 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/283e30ddfd354a30d0149a4202498271.webm?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2285250/extras/283e30ddfd354a30d0149a4202498271.mp4?t=1676352583\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
